<div class="card">
    <div class="card-body">
        <h1 class="card-title">{{title}}</h1>
        <p class="card-text">{{content}}</p>

        <h3 class="mt-4">What is Handlebars?</h3>
        <p>Handlebars is a templating engine that helps you build semantic templates effectively with no frustration. It
            provides the power necessary to let you build semantic templates based on data that is formatted as a JSON
            object.</p>

        <h3 class="mt-4">Key Features</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Simple and intuitive syntax</li>
            <li>Built-in helpers for common operations</li>
            <li>Support for custom helpers</li>
            <li>Partials for template reuse</li>
            <li>Layout support for template inheritance</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>